Jahseh Dwayne Ricardo Onfroy (Jenụwarị 23, 1998 - June 18, 2018), onye amara aha ya dị ka XXXTentacion (nke a na-akpọkarị XXXTENTACION) na nke a na-akpọkarị X, [lower-alpha 3] bụ onye America na-agụ egwú, onye na-agụ egwú na onye na-ede abụ
Ọ bụ ezie na onye na-ese okwu n'ihi nsogbu gbasara iwu ọha na eze, XXXTentacion nwetara òtù nzuzo na-eso n'etiti ndị na-eto eto ya n'oge obere ọrụ ya na ịda mbà n'obi- na egwu nkewapụ
Ndị nkatọ na ndị na-akwado ya na-etokarị ya maka ụdị egwu ya dị iche iche, yana egwu ya na-enyocha emo, drill, trap, lo-fi, indie rock, nu metal, hip hop, R&B, na rock rock
A na-ewere ya dị ka onye isi na emo rap na ụdị ụda ụda SoundCloud bụ nke dọtara nlebara anya nke ọma n'oge etiti-na-ọgwụgwụ afọ 2010,  na ọ bụ emo rapper kacha ere oge niile.
